<%= h2_with_anchor "Tabs" %>
<p>Tabs are implemented with the Stimulus.js <code>tabs_controller</code>. It works by having an list of tabs and panel targets that are hidden and shown based upon the active tab.</p>

<%= render "jumpstart/docs/snippet" do %>
<div data-controller="tabs" data-tabs-active-tab="-mb-px tab-active transition">
